Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:04.03,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}I just feel my wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.74,0:00:06.85,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}I just feel my shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.00,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}空に　rise & ride
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:24.58,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}じれったい夢だって　最初からわかってた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:30.67,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}無関心な風に　何度傷ついても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:36.19,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}太陽に手をのばす　指先のResonance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:42.27,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}瞬きのあいだも　感じたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:47.91,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}根拠なんていつも　後付けだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:55.63,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}大人ぶった予防線　飛び越えて今Bright way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:02.84,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}踏み出した空に　走っていく光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:08.56,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}一番先へ　目覚めるスピードで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:14.36,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}破れそうな鼓動　連れていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:20.19,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}もっと強い　可能性になれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:26.14,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}Rise to my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.17,0:00:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:04.03,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}I just feel my wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.74,0:00:06.85,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}I just feel my shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.00,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}向着天空 rise & ride
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:24.58,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}早知道这是个诱惑难挡的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:30.67,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}就算被漠然而至的冷风屡屡刮伤都不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:36.19,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}把手伸向太阳 手指间打出清脆回响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:42.27,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}不想错过那一眨眼的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:47.91,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}多想无益先做再说 理由事后再补就行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:55.63,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}跨越那道故作矜持的警戒线 Bright way就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:02.84,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}向着天空大步前进 追赶飞逝的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:08.56,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}用尘封已久的速度 冲到最前列
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:14.36,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}带上心中那股难以拟制的鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:20.19,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}挖掘出更强的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:26.14,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}Rise to my feet!
